data.description: Here’s the Middlefield home you’ve been looking for! Framed by woods behind on a wonderful two acre parcel, this appealing 4 bedroom, 3 bath colonial home is ready for its new owners. Over several recent years, improvements and upgrades included a new roof, rear deck, furnace, central A/C, water heater, flooring, updated bathrooms, electrical work and enhancements, septic service and Kinetico service of the water system. Bonus: Sellers are including a one-year home warranty policy. So don’t delay! Contact your favorite Realtor today for a personal showing!
